Morgan Stanley is deeply saddened to learn
that Alistair Darling passed
away on November 30, 2023. Mr. Darling had
been a member of the Board of Directors (the
“Board”) of Morgan Stanley since 2016,
and was a member of both the Audit Committee
and Risk Committee of the Board.
